channel.title: [Added] Amend URL Link For Humanitarian Clusters (Sector Vocab codelist)
channel.description: The URL link for code 10 Humanitarian Global Clusters on the [Sector Vocabulary](http://iatistandard.org/202/codelists/SectorVocabulary/) codelist is no longer valid due to a change of domains on the third party hosting site. The URL link therefore should be replaced with the following link https://data.humdata.org/dataset/standard-cluster-names-and-codes/resource/24b50d16-897b-46f9-848b-7fce08ac599b
